Docs.summary: Represents a supplier of int-valued results.

remarks.para: Represents a supplier of int-valued results. This is the int-producing primitive specialization of Supplier.
There is no requirement that a distinct result be returned each time the supplier is invoked.
This is a functional interface whose functional method is #getAsInt().
